    "b-m2-species-2": {
      "id": "b-m2-species-2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The most important technology our species is not any specific entity."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2788-wn1eyl": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2788-wn1eyl",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "It is the ability to transfer of knowledge from one mind to another, so that the next mind is able to pick up where the previous left off."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-lineage-3": {
      "id": "b-m2-lineage-3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Every leap in that technology shortened the distance between minds. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2789-zxxhcd": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2789-zxxhcd",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Writing let knowledge outlive its author"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2790-7rofu8": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2790-7rofu8",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Diagrams let it cross languages"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2791-gux0hw": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2791-gux0hw",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The internet gave everyone access to all the information around the world"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2792-is59wa": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2792-is59wa",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "AI gives us the ability to sift through the mountains of information"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp9f073-1-8ek1px": {
      "id": "pm-mrp9f073-1-8ek1px",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The human interaction surface"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2793-ig9w2s": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2793-ig9w2s",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Each step is the same move: a faster channel from one entity to another."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-two-readers-intro-4": {
      "id": "b-m2-two-readers-intro-4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "This system exists because ideas are getting more and more complex, and we need a better way of representing them and then transferring them to other people (and AI)."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2794-r7vd9e": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2794-r7vd9e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "software needs that channel — and because there are now two kinds of readers on the other end of it."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-gap-heading-5": {
      "id": "b-m2-gap-heading-5",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The gap"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-gap-physical-6": {
      "id": "b-m2-gap-physical-6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "In the physical disciplines, the knowledge is written down."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2795-jykqxb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2795-jykqxb",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A car ships with a repair manual that can walk a stranger from symptom to torque spec. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2796-juucno": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2796-juucno",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A building leaves drawings detailed enough to renovate it a century later. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2797-ciaoa3": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2797-ciaoa3",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "etc"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2798-qdefup": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2798-qdefup",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Software does not have this"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2799-ktkbyb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2799-ktkbyb",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The extent to most software is API reference"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2800-x9zuhv": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2800-x9zuhv",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "You are lucky if there is a single diagram in the docs"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-gap-excuses-7": {
      "id": "b-m2-gap-excuses-7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "There were two excuses"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2801-jxg83x": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2801-jxg83x",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The pace of change of code was near impossible to keep the docs up to date"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2802-4e88l3",
        "pm-mrp8188r-2803-9ql3fh"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2802-4e88l3": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2802-4e88l3",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Many people working on project, the intent drifts"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2803-9ql3fh": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2803-9ql3fh",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Everyone needs to know how to use the docs tools "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2804-m40s4f": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2804-m40s4f",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The tools were never built for it"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2805-i9m5xb"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2805-i9m5xb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2805-i9m5xb",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Most diagramming and docs tools are half baked as it wasn't a huge priority given the above"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2806-zetj7z": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2806-zetj7z",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Agents ended both. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2807-irnh0o": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2807-irnh0o",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Agents can easily upkeep the docs as you make changes"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2808-v73le7": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2808-v73le7",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Tooling can now be easily made as what was once a whole product, has turned into a side project"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2809-87ygvx": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2809-87ygvx",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Why we Need This"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2810-inp143": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2810-inp143",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "2 major shifts have happened with the advent of AI"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2811-8x7dtd": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2811-8x7dtd",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "One builder is now able to (and should be) working on multiple projects at a time"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2812-xaktnw": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2812-xaktnw",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The projects you work on have meaningfully scaled in complexity"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2813-vzgukk": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2813-vzgukk",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "They can carry the upkeep — and they raised the stakes, because one builder now runs several projects at once, each with the complexity that used to take a team. Comprehensive documentation stopped being a virtue. It became load-bearing."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-define-heading-8": {
      "id": "b-m2-define-heading-8",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Docs Define the Function"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-define-math-9": {
      "id": "b-m2-define-math-9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "This repository treats documentation the way mathematics treats a definition. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2814-6bacgk": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2814-6bacgk",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The docs define the function; the code is one implementation of it"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2815-d6cywe": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2815-d6cywe",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A projection of the intent into a particular language, framework, and moment. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2816-wyaeyc": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2816-wyaeyc",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Many projections satisfy the same definition. "
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2817-ppyo3v"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2817-ppyo3v": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2817-ppyo3v",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Swap the backend's language tomorrow: "
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2818-pb22wm",
        "pm-mrp8188r-2819-jyku2n"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2818-pb22wm": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2818-pb22wm",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The implementation docs are rewritten, "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2819-jyku2n": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2819-jyku2n",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The system design barely moves, and the foundation does not move at all. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2820-29ldi5": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2820-29ldi5",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The layers are ordered by how fast they are allowed to change."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-define-lossy-10": {
      "id": "b-m2-define-lossy-10",
      "type": "quote",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Code is a lossy projection of intent. Read only the code, and the why has already been projected away — every reader after you, human or agent, is left reverse-engineering what you meant."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-define-layers-11": {
      "id": "b-m2-define-layers-11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "So the corpus keeps three layers. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2821-013hxd": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2821-013hxd",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Foundation holds the intent"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2822-wkdlah"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2822-wkdlah": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2822-wkdlah",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "What this is and why it exists. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2823-bturf9": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2823-bturf9",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "System Design holds the behavior"
        }
      ],
      "children": [
        "pm-mrp8188r-2824-fbonl6"
      ]
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2824-fbonl6": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2824-fbonl6",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "What the system does, independent of any codebase."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2825-mnqmwr": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2825-mnqmwr",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {
        "ordered": true
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Implementation describes the current projection, and is allowed to churn. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2826-c7p4fu": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2826-c7p4fu",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A reader starts at the top and descends only as far as the task requires."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-define-obligation-12": {
      "id": "b-m2-define-obligation-12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "A definition implies an obligation"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2827-a9pkca": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2827-a9pkca",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "If the docs say what the system should do, the system must be held to them. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2828-vhnu8s": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2828-vhnu8s",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "This corpus already keeps itself mechanically honest — every document's bytes and rendered markdown are pinned by tests — and behavior-level verification against the docs is the frontier this project is walking toward."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-trust-heading-13": {
      "id": "b-m2-trust-heading-13",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Trust is the point"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-trust-chain-14": {
      "id": "b-m2-trust-chain-14",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Agents write more of the code every month. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2829-reu0y5": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2829-reu0y5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "That only scales on trust, and trust does not come from reviewing diffs faster. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2830-shybmt": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2830-shybmt",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "It comes from the behavior and its reasoning being locked in"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2831-6q1jmq": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2831-6q1jmq",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "This is what the piece does, this is why it is this way"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2832-5fbk24": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2832-5fbk24",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "These are the decisions you do not quietly change. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2833-gvlrua": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2833-gvlrua",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Written down, that turns autonomy from drift into expansion — the system builds on your design decisions instead of guessing past them."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-trust-slop-15": {
      "id": "b-m2-trust-slop-15",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Slop is what intent transfer looks like when it fails. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2834-bpmkij": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2834-bpmkij",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "An agent that cannot find the why fills the gap with plausible guesses, and plausible guesses compound. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2835-mckutg": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2835-mckutg",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The fix is not a stricter reviewer at the end of the pipeline; it is a sharper definition at the top. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp8188r-2836-i017ic": {
      "id": "pm-mrp8188r-2836-i017ic",
      "type": "list-item",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "Defining the identity of the software — exactly, durably, in a form both kinds of readers consume well — is the work this system is built for."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-divider-21": {
      "id": "b-m2-divider-21",
      "type": "divider",
      "props": {},
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-conviction-heading-22": {
      "id": "b-m2-conviction-heading-22",
      "type": "heading",
      "props": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The conviction"
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-conviction-durable-23": {
      "id": "b-m2-conviction-durable-23",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The docs are the durable artifact. The code is the current projection. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp825fl-2842-dmjbpr": {
      "id": "pm-mrp825fl-2842-dmjbpr",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "When they disagree, the right question is not which file is newer — it is where the intent is most clearly preserved."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-conviction-bet-24": {
      "id": "b-m2-conviction-bet-24",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "When a better model arrives next year, hand it Foundation and System Design and you should get a better implementation back, with nothing lost in the handoff. "
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "pm-mrp825fl-2843-ctj9xb": {
      "id": "pm-mrp825fl-2843-ctj9xb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "That is the bet: intent outlives any one projection."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    "b-m2-credits-25": {
      "id": "b-m2-credits-25",
